node.text: We’re longtime admirers of artist and textile designer Élan Byrd and her organic, natural fiber work, so we’re happy to announce a rug capsule designed exclusively for us. The @elanbyrd line will focus on rich texture and slow, intentional construction. Head to our link in bio for more!
